src:
Trumps stabschef har kallats till riksrättsförhör
Vita husets stabschef Mick Mulvaney har kallats till representanthuset för att ge vittnesmål till den utredning som Demokraterna där driver för att eventuellt inleda ett riksrättsmål mot USA:s president Donald Trump.
05 Nov 2019, 19:42 by TT

text:
Trump's chief of staff has been called to court hearings
White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney has been called to the House of Representatives to give testimony to the investigation that the Democrats are running to possibly launch a national court case against US President Donald Trump.
05 Nov 2019, 19:42 by TT
